    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Shopify version of instasearch\r\n----\r\n\r\nLooks like this is a bug in instasearch **v1**, but not in **v2** as this works: \r\n https://codesandbox.io/s/1rvmqq5jm4\r\n\r\nBut it does not work on my version. \r\n\r\n\r\nv2  {{ '//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/instantsearch.js@2/dist/instantsearch.min.js' | script_tag }} \r\nv1  {{ '//cdn.jsdelivr.net/instantsearch.js/1/instantsearch.min.js' | script_tag }} \r\n\r\nDocs issue v1/v2\r\n---\r\nDocs for facetsExcludes say \" Each facet must be properly defined in the facets attribute.\"\r\nSee https://community.algolia.com/algoliasearch-helper-js/reference.html#SearchParameters#facetsExcludes\r\n\r\nbut this works without  the facets attribute in v2 of instasearch :  https://codesandbox.io/s/1rvmqq5jm4\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n  searchParameters: {\r\n    facetsExcludes: {\r\n      brand: [\"Sony\"]\r\n    },\r\n    hitsPerPage: 8\r\n  }\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
