    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "While this clearly is something that is going wrong, you can use `transformItems` to hide an item from a list, instead of doing it with helper parameters:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n  instantsearch.widgets.refinementList({\r\n    container: '#brand-list',\r\n    attributeName: 'brand',\r\n    transformItems: items => items.filter(item => item.label !== 'Sony'),\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```\r\n\r\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/8k9wqo53pl?module=%2Fsrc%2Fapp.js",
