    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Re-open - workaround\r\n---\r\n\r\n@Haroenv The issue is not about hiding. it is about combining disjunctive facets with excluded facets (.facetsExcludes). Please re-open, maybe someone will post a workaround.\r\n\r\nI suspect some workaround is possible. The facetsExcludes is only needed when no disjunctive facet items are selected, when a disjunctive facet item is selected facetsExcludes is not required.\r\n\r\nHide facets item\r\n---\r\nThis worked, but did not help. I was hoping it would solve another issue with \"Show More\".\r\n\"Show more\" shows the items in the facetsExcludes, which I did not want. So I just got rid of the show more for now.\r\n\r\nInstant Search v2\r\n---\r\n@pagealexandre  looking foward to IS2. Looks to fix several on my current issues.\r\n\r\nI did try switching to IS2, is it possible?. It looks like a lot of work. Am not sure if it is even possible to switch but am keen to use it. \r\n ",
